text:
@VenomousWoe

I never felt that the traveling was pointless. It ultimately does serve the purpose of getting to the colossi, without it you would have a series of boss battles with nothing in between. Besides, I always enjoy exploring the worlds that team Ico produces.

And I also dug the horse control scheme, particularly the way that it was more like directing than controlling. You may read that as drunken, but I always felt that the horse worked with me, not against me.
